d (distilled) to create another one. We demonstrate how the metric can be used to inform a more meaningful debate about AI strategies and cost. Te novelty of the approach is that it can be used to reason about strategies and trade-offs across the life cycle and’supply-chain’ of models. © 2023 Copyright held by the owner/author(s).},
